## Common Gotchas

- Unique constraint: Add @@unique([userId, productId]) to Review model
- Rating recalculation: Aggregate on write or use materialized view
- XSS prevention: Never use dangerouslySetInnerHTML, sanitize input
- Moderation: Consider auto-approve for verified purchasers

## Test Flows

1. Submit review → appears in moderation queue
2. Approve review → appears on product page
3. Submit second review same product → error (unique)
4. Update rating → average recalculated
5. Mark as helpful → count incremented
